      <div class="model-card"><h3>Profile 30" single built-in wall oven</h3><p>Standard 30" cabinet cutout single-cavity. True European Convection + SmartHQ + Air Fry. Service: bake element, third-element, convection fan, control board, sensors, door hardware.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Profile 30" double built-in wall oven</h3><p>Stacked dual-cavity configuration. Upper + lower independent elements + sensors. Shared primary control board with dual-cavity coordination.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>True European Convection third-element</h3><p>Dedicated heating element around convection fan heats circulating air directly. Distinct failure mode from main bake element — requires specific diagnostic.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>SmartHQ Wi-Fi integration</h3><p>App pairing, remote monitoring, firmware updates. Most smart-feature issues resolve at firmware + network layer without hardware replacement.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Air Fry mode</h3><p>Cooking mode using existing convection hardware at high-speed + high-temp settings. Service issues usually trace to underlying convection components.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Self-clean cycle</h3><p>Standard pyrolytic self-clean. Door-lock motor, thermal sensor, cycle firmware. Lower cycle temperature than Fisher & Paykel's 900°F pyrolytic.</p></div>
